2. Gate the Content Strategically
While some content should be freely accessible, gating your webinar replay with a simple form allows you to capture high-intent leads. You can then route these leads into nurturing sequences, retargeting campaigns, or direct sales outreach.

We help businesses decide when to gate, how much to gate, and how to segment those leads for maximum efficiency.

3. Use Intent Data for Smart Promotion
Not all leads are created equal. Using intent data, we promote your on-demand webinars to users who are actively researching similar topics, showing purchase intent, or engaging with competitor content.

This ensures your replays are getting in front of the right eyes at the right time—no wasted impressions, no cold traffic.

